            <title>[LU-3515] What do the &quot;osp-pre&quot; and &quot;osp-syn&quot; threads do?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3515</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m curious what the &quot;osp-pre&quot; and &quot;osp-syn&quot; threads are for, can anybody give me a quick over view? I see nearly 800 of them on our Grove MDS, and that seems like far too many threads to be sane, so I&apos;m curious what their purpose is.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
